Imran Nazir retired hurt on 5* from 6/1 to 104/6 (struck on forearm)
Imran Nazir/Shahid Afridi 1st wicket partnership 3 runs in 8 minutes from 13 balls
Imran Nazir/Yousuf Youhana 2nd wicket partnership 3 runs in 11 minutes from 16 balls
Pakistan 50 in 60 minutes from 81 balls

Younis Khan/Shoaib Malik 5th wicket partnership 3 runs in 8 minutes from 12 balls
Pakistan 100 in 144 minutes from 201 balls
Shoaib Malik/Rashid Latif 6th wicket partnership 26 runs in 41 minutes from 62 balls
Imran Nazir/Shoaib Malik 7th wicket partnership 20 runs in 20 minutes from 32 balls
Pakistan 150 in 190 minutes from 272 balls
Imran Nazir/Wasim Akram 8th wicket partnership 29 runs in 21 minutes from 32 balls
Imran Nazir/Waqar Younis 9th wicket partnership 23* runs in 18 minutes from 28 balls
Pakistan's innings ended at 5.46pm
Pakistan's innings of 176/8 was the lowest team total recorded at Colonial Stadium in ODIs (previous: 198/9 (48ov) Australia v South Africa, 3rd ODI, 2000/01)
Australia 50 in 47 minutes from 64 balls
AC Gilchrist/ML Hayden 1st wicket partnership 50 runs in 47 minutes from 64 balls
Gilchrist 50 in 70 minutes from 42 balls
Australia 100 in 72 minutes from 97 balls

Attendance: 11,681
The match ended at 9.04pm
